    UTF-8 string           | string          | 0x78

    UTF-8 string           | string          | 0x79

    UTF-8 string           | string          | 0x7A

    UTF-8 string           | string          | 0x7B

    UTF-8 string           | string          | 0x7F

    array                  | array           | 0x80..0x97

    array                  | array           | 0x98

    array                  | array           | 0x99

    array                  | array           | 0x9A

    array                  | array           | 0x9B

    array                  | array           | 0x9F

    map                    | object          | 0xA0..0xB7

    map                    | object          | 0xB8

    map                    | object          | 0xB9

    map                    | object          | 0xBA

    map                    | object          | 0xBB

    map                    | object          | 0xBF

    False                  | `false`         | 0xF4

    True                   | `true`          | 0xF5

    Null                   | `null`          | 0xF6

